title: Report: Prudential’s $2.35B acquisition of Seattle insurance tech startup Assurance has gone ‘sour’ - GeekWire
content: Report: Prudential’s $2.35B acquisition of Seattle insurance tech startup Assurance has gone ‘sour’  GeekWire
description: Wally Gobetz) When Prudential Financial acquired Seattle-area startup Assurance IQ for $2.35 billion in September 2019, the deal was heralded as one of the largest acquisitions in Seattle tech history.
